{
  "chapter": 48,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十九回 长街之遇。寒冬大雪笼罩武汉三镇，飞龙镖局群集长江北岸，龙形八掌檀明因十年前旧案重翻，英雄地位动摇。裴珏在冷谷双木陪伴下抵达长街，万人空巷高呼\"裴大先生\"。与此同时，东方五剑自江南渡江而来，因东方震即将迎娶檀文琪，与裴珏形成微妙对峙。暗中有人（疑为战飞安排）当街高喊挑拨，质问裴珏是否因青梅竹马被夺而愤怒，又讽刺东方世家攀附檀家。东方五剑中最年轻的东方湖怒而拔剑，要与裴珏单独较量。裴珏虽心头热血上涌，仍保持克制，表示不愿被暗中破坏者得逞。东方铁试图调解，但局面愈发紧张，众人被层层围住，进退两难。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生午前可到！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？是谁来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东方五剑！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前面的是裴珏！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸会幸会！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "东方五剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸会幸会！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生，你的童年爱侣被人抢走了，你心里难道一点也不难受？难道一点也不愤怒？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "东方震",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东方震，檀文琪虽然嫁给你，但她的心里还是爱着裴大先生的，你觉得这滋味好受么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "东方震",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄别来可好？闻道近来裴兄技艺大进，小弟想来，也高兴得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你高兴什么！裴大先生哪点不比你兄弟五人强？只可叹檀明竟为了要巴结你家，却将他女儿当做了礼物，牺牲了他女儿的一生幸福，东方震呀东方震，你说是不是这么回事呀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪位朋友要想说话，不妨到这里来说个明白，这样——",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你兄弟五人有个好爸爸，又都有个好师傅，我们心里虽然气愤，可也惹不起你们。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连龙形八掌都要拍你们的马屁，只可惜裴大先生一表人材，文武双全，就因为没有后台，竟被人拆散鸳鸯。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "暗中呼喊者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "飞灵堡一向以侠义自居，想不到竟做出了这样的事来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这些无耻的小人，可是阁下安排在路上的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "五弟！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "兄台的话，兄弟有些听不懂。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我东方湖不凭师门，不仗父兄，倒要单独与你这裴大先生斗上一斗，看你到底有什么惊人的文才武艺？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "五弟，你这是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打！打！就打死这小子，看他的师傅、父兄怎么样？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄，这究竟是怎么一回事？但请兄台解释一句。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "兄台要我解释，我却还不知道要谁解释呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "在下不愿与兄台们相争，一来是为了与兄台们素无仇怨，再来却是不愿被这般暗中破坏之人如愿；但兄台却不可欺人太甚，至少也该将事情判断清楚才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄弟此次渡江北来，亦不过是为了要将事情查问清楚，并非绝对要与檀家结下亲事，但兄台——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "兄台们是否要与檀文琪结亲，与我又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "没有关系么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    }
  ],
